# MSBuild / C++/WinRT build output. The shipped binaries live in
# packages/nativescript-masonkit/platforms/windows (committed during local dev, or pulled from
# NuGet by npm consumers); everything matched here is regenerated by publish.ps1 / Mason.sln.
bin/
obj/
# Default per-config / per-arch output + intermediate dirs (any depth).
x64/
ARM64/
Debug/
Release/
# cppwinrt / mdmerge generated artifacts.
Generated Files/
Merged/
Unmerged/
# cppwinrt shortens the per-project intermediate dir to NativeSc.<guid8> at the project root.
NativeSc.*/
*.winmd
*.tlog
*.obj
*.pdb
*.ipdb
*.iobj
*.pch
*.exp
*.ilk
*.lib
*.pri
*.rsp
